export default "Delete a node, a connection or clear cache\n------------------------------------------\n\nSyntax\n------\nDelete a node\n```\ndelete node {name}\n```\n\nDelete the connections between two nodes if any\n```\ndelete connection {nodeA} and {nodeB}\n```\n\nClear cache for API fetchers\n```\nclear cache\n```\n\nAlias\n-----\n`clear` is an alias of `delete`\n"